node.text:
I was excited to receive this amazing cordless stick vacuum from @moosoo_us! There’s so much to love about this vacuum, but what I love about it the most is the price! And if you use my code 【decorforkid】you will get an additional 15% off on the MOOSOO shop. Link to shop is in @moosoo_us bio
#moosoo #dfkpartner

Moosoo offical website is now live!Ten Lucky Moosoo Lovers will get our Popular D601 FOR FREE!!!
Here's how to enter:

1. Follow us and @Moosoo_us
2.Comment & Like this Post 🏻
3.Tag 2 friends in the comments.👥 That's it! Good Luck & I hope you alllll are staying safe☺️ Giveaway will end on May 31 and will be announced on @moosoo_us page!
